Yocto configuration for aria-g25/Atmel at91sam9g25
--------------------------------------------------

* Download yocto https://www.yoctoproject.org/download/yocto-project-13-poky-80 and extract

* git clone git://github.com/baseapp/meta-atmel.git -b yocto

* Edit conf/bblayers.conf in this repo to match yocto and meta-atmel paths
  Also edit local.conf, see https://www.yoctoproject.org/docs/current/yocto-project-qs/yocto-project-qs.html

* cd /path-to/yocto/poky; . ./oe-init-build-env /path-to/this-repo/aria-g25/

* bitbake core-image-minimal
